name: Tribble Icons
effect:
REVERSEReverse the direction of play.
SKIPSkip the next player.
GOTake another turn.
DISCARD Discard any one card from your hand.
POISONChoose an opponent to discard the top card of their
deck. Score points equal to that number of tribbles.
RESCUERecover any card from your discard pile to the top
of your deck (or if it's playable, you may play it).
CLONEThis card may be played even when it has the
same number of Tribbles as the last card played.
BONUSIf you get all four Bonus cards (1-10-100-1,000)
in your play pile, score an extra 100,000 points.
